CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTION

January 19, 2007

[Cite as 0111912007 Case Announcements, 2007-0hio-162.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-2299. Biros v. Houk.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition for writ of habeas corpus of Kenneth Biros and petitioner’s motion to supplement petition for writ of habeas corpus and affidavit. Motion to supplement petition granted. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger and Cdpp, JJ., concur.
